/*
DECLARE @in_standort varchar(36) 
DECLARE @in_gebaeude varchar(36) 
DECLARE @in_geschoss varchar(36) 
DECLARE @in_trakt varchar(36) 
DECLARE @in_haus varchar(36) 
DECLARE @in_raum varchar(36) 

SET @in_standort = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' 
SET @in_gebaeude = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' 
SET @in_geschoss = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' 
SET @in_trakt = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' 
SET @in_haus = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' 
SET @in_raum = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' 
*/
/*
SELECT '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' AS RPT_AL_UID, 'Alle' AS RPT_Name, -999 AS RPT_Sort 

UNION 
*/
SELECT 
	 AL_UID AS RPT_AL_UID
	,AL_Name_DE AS RPT_Name
	,AL_Sort_DE AS RPT_Sort 
FROM V_RPT_SEL_AL_Anlage

WHERE (1=1) 
/*
AND
(
	AL_SO_UID = @in_standort 
	OR 
	'00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' = @in_standort 
)
*/
AND
(
	AL_GB_UID = @in_gebaeude 
	OR 
	'00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' = @in_gebaeude 
)
/*
AND
(
	AL_GS_UID = @in_geschoss 
	OR 
	'00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' = @in_geschoss 
)

AND
(
	AL_RM_UID = @in_raum 
	OR 
	'00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' = @in_raum 
)

AND
(
	(
		CASE WHEN @in_raum = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' 
				AND @in_geschoss = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' 
				AND @in_gebaeude = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' 
				AND @in_standort = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' 
			THEN 0
			ELSE 1
		END
	) = 1
)
*/
AND 
( 
	( @in_groups = '0000') 
	OR
	(
		SELECT 
			ISNULL(SUM(CAST(ALR_IsRead AS int)), 0) AS ALR_IsRead 
		FROM T_SYS_Anlagerechte 
		WHERE (1=1) 
		AND T_SYS_Anlagerechte.ALR_AL_UID = V_RPT_SEL_AL_Anlage.AL_UID 
		AND @in_groups LIKE '%,' + CAST(T_SYS_Anlagerechte.ALR_GRANTEE_ID AS varchar(36)) + ',%' 
	) > 0 
)


ORDER BY RPT_Sort

SELECT     RPT_UID, RPT_Lang, RPT_Sort_Alpha_ASC AS RPT_Sort
FROM         dbo.tfu_RPT_SEL_Alle(@in_mandant, @in_sprache) AS tfu_RPT_SEL_Alle_1

/*
UNION

SELECT     RPT_UID, RPT_Name_Beta AS RPT_Lang, RPT_Sort
FROM         dbo.tfu_RPT_SEL_Standort(@in_mandant, @in_sprache, @in_groups) AS tfu_RPT_SEL_Standort_1
ORDER BY RPT_Sort
*/

SELECT     RPT_UID, RPT_Lang, RPT_Sort_Alpha_ASC AS RPT_Sort
FROM         dbo.tfu_RPT_SEL_Alle(@in_mandant, @in_sprache) AS tfu_RPT_SEL_Alle_1
UNION
SELECT     RPT_UID, RPT_Name_Beta, RPT_Sort
--FROM         dbo.tfu_RPT_SEL_Gebaeude(@in_mandant, @in_sprache, @in_standort, @in_groups) AS tfu_RPT_SEL_Gebaeude_1
FROM dbo.tfu_RPT_SEL_Gebaeude_AllOnAll(@in_mandant, @in_sprache, @in_standort, @in_groups)  AS tfu_RPT_SEL_Gebaeude_1
ORDER BY RPT_Sort

SELECT 
	 RPT_UID 
	,RPT_MDT_ID 
	,RPT_Nr 
	,RPT_Code 
	,RPT_Kurz 
	,RPT_Lang 
	,RPT_Sort 
FROM tfu_RPT_SEL_Alle(@in_mandant, @in_sprache) 

/*
UNION 


SELECT 
	 RPT_UID 
	,RPT_MDT_ID 
	,RPT_Nr 
	,RPT_Code 
	,RPT_Kurz 
	,LTRIM(RTRIM( ISNULL(RPT_Lang, '') + ' ' + ISNULL(RPT_Nr, '') )) AS RPT_Name 
	,RPT_Sort 
FROM tfu_RPT_SEL_Geschoss(@in_mandant, @in_sprache, @in_gebaeude, @in_groups) 

ORDER BY RPT_Sort
*/

/*
DECLARE @in_sprache varchar(2) 
SET @in_sprache = 'DE'

DECLARE @in_stichtag datetime
SET @in_stichtag = GETDATE()

DECLARE @in_anlage varchar(36) 
SET @in_anlage = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' 

DECLARE @in_gebaeude varchar(36) 
SET @in_gebaeude = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' 
*/


SELECT '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' AS RPT_AL_UID, 'nur Anlage' AS RPT_Name, 99999 AS RPT_Sort 

UNION 


SELECT 
	 AL_UID AS RPT_AL_UID 
	,AL_Nr + ' (' + AK_Lang + ')' AS RPT_Name 
	,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY AL_Nr + ' (' + AK_Lang + ')') AS RPT_Sort 
FROM tfu_RPT_SEL_Anlage(@in_sprache, getdate()) 
WHERE AL_IsBauteil = 1 

/*
AND AL_UID IN 
(
SELECT BP_Objekt_UID 
FROM T_UPS_BudgetPositionen 
WHERE T_UPS_BudgetPositionen.BP_Status = 1 
)
*/

AND
(
	Main_AL_UID = @in_anlage 
	OR 
	 '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' = @in_anlage 
)

/*
AND
(
	GB_UID = @in_gebaeude 
	OR 
	'00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' = @in_gebaeude 
)
*/
ORDER BY RPT_Sort

SELECT    RPT_UID AS RPT_BPK_UID, RPT_Lang AS RPT_Aufwandskonto_Kurz, RPT_Lang  AS RPT_Aufwandskonto_Lang, -99 AS RPT_Sort
FROM         dbo.tfu_RPT_SEL_Alle(@in_mandant, @in_sprache) AS tfu_RPT_SEL_Alle_1
UNION
SELECT 
	 RPT_BPK_UID
	,RPT_Aufwandskonto_Kurz
                ,RPT_Aufwandskonto_Lang
	,RPT_Sort
FROM tfu_RPT_SEL_UPS_Baukostenplan(@in_mandant, @in_sprache, 0) 


WHERE 
(

RPT_BPK_UID IN 
(
	SELECT ISNULL(BP_BKP_UID, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000') 
	FROM tfu_RPT_AL_Anlagenblatt(@in_mandant, @in_sprache, @in_jahr, @in_gebaeude, @in_anlage, @in_bauteil) 
)
OR

RPT_BPK_UID = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
)

ORDER BY RPT_Sort, RPT_Aufwandskonto_Lang

Public Function GetDateForCulture(ByVal iDay As Integer, ByVal iMonthNum As Integer, ByVal iYear As Integer, ByVal strReportLanguage As String) As String
        Dim strReturnValue As String = ""
        Try
            strReportLanguage = strReportLanguage.ToLower()

            'Dim dtThisDateDate As DateTime = DateTime.Now
            'Dim dtThisDateDate As New DateTime(2010, 12, 31)
            Dim dtThisDateDate As New DateTime(iYear, iMonthNum, iDay)

            Dim strCultureString As String = ""
            Select Case strReportLanguage
                Case "de"
                    strCultureString = "de-ch"
                Case "fr"
                    strCultureString = "fr-ch"
                Case "it"
                    strCultureString = "it-ch"
                Case "en"
                    strCultureString = "en-us"
                Case Else
                    strCultureString = strReportLanguage
            End Select

            Dim ci As New System.Globalization.CultureInfo(strCultureString)

            Dim strFormat = ci.DateTimeFormat.LongDatePattern
            If ci.CompareInfo.IndexOf(strFormat, "dddd, ", System.Globalization.CompareOptions.IgnoreCase) > -1 Then
                strFormat = Mid(ci.DateTimeFormat.LongDatePattern, Len("dddd, ") + 1)
            End If

            strReturnValue = dtThisDateDate.ToString(strFormat, ci)
            'strReturnValue = System.Globalization.CultureInfo.CurrentCulture.TextInfo.ToTitleCase(strReturnValue)
            strReturnValue = ci.TextInfo.ToTitleCase(strReturnValue)
        Catch ex As Exception
            strReturnValue = iDay.ToString().PadLeft(2, "0") + "." + iMonthNum.ToString().PadLeft(2, "0") + "." + iYear.ToString()
        End Try

        Return strReturnValue
    End Function
